Using Remix

Open Remix IDE : https://remix.ethereum.org

Use the simple storage contract

Compile the contract

Have a look at the abi and the bytecode, do you understand how the abi relates to your contract's code ?

-----ABI as follow-----

[
	{
		"inputs": [                                     //dev Store value in variable
			{
				"internalType": "uint256",
				"name": "num",                              //param num value to store
				"type": "uint256"
			}
		],
		"name": "store",
		"outputs": [],
		"stateMutability": "nonpayable",
		"type": "function"
	},
	{
		"inputs": [],                                   //dev retrieve value
		"name": "retrieve",
		"outputs": [                                    //return value of 'number'
			{
				"internalType": "uint256",
				"name": "",
				"type": "uint256"
			}
		],
		"stateMutability": "view",
		"type": "function"
	}
]

